a, you will find this book invaluable.Scott Oaks is a senior software engineer for the Java Performance Engineering group at Sun Microsystems and the author of four books in the O\'Reilly Java series.Formerly a senior systems engineer at Sun Microsystems, Henry Wong is an independent consultant working on various Java related projects.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=r8hhO7oGKrEC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api',361,'2004-09-10','978-1-5499-3173-4'),(791,'Stephen Hawking','The Encyclopaedia Britannica: Ita to Lor',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=4KVV1x0q8KUC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',1038,'1911-01-01','978-1-6770-6692-6'),(792,'Hugh Chisholm','The Encyclopaedia Britannica',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=7T8OAQAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',1016,'1911-01-01','978-1-85672-976-5'),(793,'Arthur Mee','China. Pacific and Indian Oceans. Australia. India. Central Asia',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=tHBKAQAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',774,'1908-01-01','978-1-307-10534-6'),(794,'V.S. Naipaul','Facts about Sugar',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=QI0eAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',624,'1923-01-01','978-0-11-033344-1'),(795,'Peter Verhas','Java 9 Programming By Example','Get the steps you need to discover the world of Java 9 programming using real-world examples About This Book We bridge the gap between “learning” and “doing” by providing real-world examples that will improve your software development Our example-based approach will get you started quickly with software programming, get you up-to-speed with Java 9, and improve your Java skills This book will show you the best practices of Java coding and improve your productivity Who This Book Is For This book is for anyone who wants to learn the Java programming language. You are expected to have some prior programming experience w